@startuml
title Tenant Lifecycle State Machine

[*] --> provisioning : Admin creates tenant
provisioning --> active : Key generated,\nnamespace allocated
active --> suspended : Payment fail /\nadmin action
suspended --> active : Payment resolved
active --> deleted : Admin deletes tenant
suspended --> deleted : Admin deletes tenant

state provisioning : [entry] generate LiteLLM virtual key\n[entry] create Pinecone namespace\n[entry] assign Telegram bot token
state active : Can receive messages,\nrespond to queries\n[do] RAG + memory + LLM
state suspended : Bot returns\noffline message\n[do] Block LiteLLM key
state deleted : All data removed\n(Pinecone namespace,\nmemories, LiteLLM key\ncleaned up)

note right of provisioning : /api/admin/provision
note right of suspended : litellm_admin_service.block_key()
note right of deleted : Tenant record may be\nretained or soft-deleted

@enduml
